data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!!!This is a MUST see home featuring 3 BR, 2 BA with TONS of parking and outdoor storage and upgrades!! Great Open Floorplan, Granite Countertops, 10' ceilings, Beautiful trim work throughout, Bullnose corners, Coffered Ceiling in Primary BR. Own an RV???? No problem! The sellers have added RV hook-ups!. This home has the perfect "country setting" yet only a short drive to the beach! Book your showing today before this one is gone!
